            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="rounded-full bg-[#f8623a] text-[#2d2d2d] font-bold tracking-widest px-8 py-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
            data-umami-event="cta_try_web_app"
          >
            try the web app â†’
