            <p class="text-[#ebebe6]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">running balances and payment history across every client. no surprises.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal bg-[#232323] border border-[#ebebe6]/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#f8623a]/40 transition-colors group">
            <div class="text-[#f8623a] mb-5">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/>
                <path d="M9 16l2 2 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold tracking-widest text-[#ebebe6] mb-3 group-hover:text-[#f8623a] transition-colors">every session, in one place</h3>
            <p class="text-[#ebebe6]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">client roster, upcoming sessions, punch card status â€” one tap away.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal bg-[#232323] border border-[#ebebe6]/10 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#f8623a]/40 transition-colors group">
            <div class="text-[#f8623a] mb-5">
